<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="561" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="8.[2031,2617,1935,2362]" pageId="8" pageNumber="561">
This skunk has been classified as a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName box="[2197,2432,2058,2087]" class="Mammalia" family="Mephitidae" genus="Spilogale" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Carnivora" pageId="8" pageNumber="561" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="putorius">Spilogale putorius</taxonomicName>
